me all right, what I really,

00:18:20.970 --> 00:18:24.890
I did that honestly so that Kristen
and her director could hear it

00:18:24.890 --> 00:18:27.670
in case they were like oh God don't
sing that tonight, don't do that.

00:18:27.670 --> 00:18:30.730
But fortunately they were both
like oh my God, you have to.

00:18:30.730 --> 00:18:32.850
So I went and I sang it you know,

00:18:32.850 --> 00:18:35.370
like I said Kristen's show
was all sort of sparkles

00:18:35.370 --> 00:18:40.360
and you know soprano and
popular and all of that stuff.

00:18:40.360 --> 00:18:43.880
And then she sang 50 Years
Long which is a you know kind

00:18:43.880 --> 00:18:46.780
