then she introduced me and asked me

00:18:46.780 --> 00:18:48.970
to come out on stage and I did.

00:18:48.970 --> 00:18:53.660
And I said, I wrote
this this morning.

00:18:53.660 --> 00:18:55.410
I don't know what to tell you.

00:18:55.410 --> 00:18:59.570
This was the best I could
do and so I sang the song.

00:18:59.570 --> 00:19:01.480
And I couldn't tell, you
know, there's a couple

00:19:01.480 --> 00:19:03.300
