00:20:03.620 --> 00:20:05.080
&gt;&gt; What is your relation,
both of you,

00:20:05.080 --> 00:20:06.720
your relationship with an audience?

00:20:06.720 --> 00:20:10.340
How does that effect you, influence
you, change your performance?

