convince them or win them over

00:20:27.480 --> 00:20:30.600
or impress them or get a
certain type of reaction.

00:20:30.600 --> 00:20:33.170
Now when I come out my only
intention is to connect.

00:20:33.170 --> 00:20:37.160
So regardless of the material,
if it's mine, if it's not,

00:20:37.160 --> 00:20:43.680
