certainly fuels the fire.

00:21:10.160 --> 00:21:16.240
And when they are not it's
a challenge to keep grounded

00:21:16.240 --> 00:21:19.650
and keep doing you know keep giving
your blood and your heart the way

00:21:19.650 --> 00:21:22.230
that you would if they
were enthusiastic about it.

